  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110103180474\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110103180474\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p>이수한의원 부설 '이수 한의학연구소'가 설립되었습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>대학원과 연구원시절 못다한 연구들을 진행하기 위해 아직은 보잘것 없지만 </p>\r\n<p>미래를 내다보면서 설립했습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>진단 및 치료를 위한 여러가지 연구 및 개발을 통해 </p>\r\n<p>보다 더 좋은 의료 서비스를 제공하고자 합니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>감사합니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 이수한의원 원장 및 직원 일동 -</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20110217_138/isuhani_1297916675079xfcRs_JPEG/%C0%CC%BC%F6_%C7%D1%C0%C7%C7%D0%BF%AC%B1%B8%BC%D2_%BB%E7%BE%F7%C0%DA%B5%EE%B7%CF%C1%F5_%BC%F6%C1%A4.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20110217_138/isuhani_1297916675079xfcRs_JPEG/%C0%CC%BC%F6_%C7%D1%C0%C7%C7%D0%BF%AC%B1%B8%BC%D2_%BB%E7%BE%F7%C0%DA%B5%EE%B7%CF%C1%F5_%BC%F6%C1%A4.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A2A934BA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20110217_138/isuhani_1297916675079xfcRs_JPEG/%C0%CC%BC%F6_%C7%D1%C0%C7%C7%D0%BF%AC%B1%B8%BC%D2_%BB%E7%BE%F7%C0%DA%B5%EE%B7%CF%C1%F5_%BC%F6%C1%A4.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
